ning Season”的表演拉开了演出的帷幕， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">Raye</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-announces-final-headliner-3591184">Tate McRae</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-announces-more-live-performers-for-2024-ceremony-3587758">Jungle、Rema、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-announces-becky-hill-and-chase-status-collab-performance-3588553">Becky Hill 和 Chase &amp; Status</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/calvin-harris-ellie-goulding-confirmed-to-perform-at-brit-awards-2024-3590433">Calvin Harris 和 Ellie Goulding</a>也进行了进一步的表演。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kylie-minogue">凯莉·米洛 (Kylie Minogue)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kylie-minogue-to-receive-brits-global-icon-award-and-perform-at-ceremony-3586464">荣获今年的全英音乐奖全球偶像奖</a>，她将以自己的现场表演结束这场演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bring-me-the-horizons-sweary-acceptance-speech-at-the-brits-2024-3595779">《Watch Bring Me The Horizo​​n》在 2024 年全英音乐奖上脏兮兮的获奖感言</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
