聆听 Lykke Li 深情翻唱 Johnny Cash 的《Ring Of Fire》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-lykke-lis-soulful-cover-of-johnny-cashs-ring-of-fire-3595762?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to- lykke-lis-soulful-cover-of-johnny-cashs-ring-of-fire（火环）Max Pilley Sat, 02 Mar 2024 19:37:33 +0000 Music NewsNewsCountryPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3595762 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="lykke li getty 图片 keith Mayhew" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这是她两年来的第一首新音乐，取自 Netflix 新电影《少女》的原声带</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-lykke-lis-soulful-cover-of-johnny-cashs-ring-of-fire-3595762">《聆听 Lykke Li 深情翻唱 Johnny Cash 的《Ring Of Fire》》一文</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="lykke li getty 图片 keith Mayhew" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/lykke-li-getty-images-keith-mayhew-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lykke-li">Lykke Li</a>带着她两年来的第一首新音乐回归，翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/johnny-cash">Johnny Cash</a>的《Ring of Fire》——请听下面的曲目。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="342" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/lykke-li-soundtrack-of-my-life-3230203"><b>我的生活原声带：Lykke Li</b></a></li></ul><p>这首歌是为<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>黑暗奇幻电影《<em>少女》</em>录制的原声带，由胡安·卡洛斯·弗雷斯纳迪罗执导，<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/millie-bobby-brown">米莉·博比·布朗</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ray-winstone">雷·温斯顿</a>和安吉拉·贝塞特主演。</p><p>谈到重新诠释卡什 1963 年的单曲，李告诉<a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/news/lykke-li-johnny-cash-ring-of-fire-cover-netflix-damsel-1235926205/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Variety</i></a> ：“说实话，我一生中听过的唯一版本是约翰尼·卡什版本，所以我没有真正的历史。我只是一片空白。我坐在钢琴前，从我嘴里说出的第一句话就是我录制的内容。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Lykke Li 的《火环》 |少女|官方原声带 | Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WeQimagM-tM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这首歌由琼·卡特·卡什 (June Carter Cash) 和梅尔·基尔戈尔 (Merle Kilgore) 创作，并由琼·卡特 (June Carter Cash) 的妹妹安妮塔·卡特 (Anita Carter) 首次录制。李谈到了她从得知这首歌曲是卡什的搭档创作后所获得的具体影响。</p><p> “我受到琼·卡特的启发，”她解释道。 “我读到的是，当他们都与其他人结婚时，她写下了这篇文章，她当时想，妈的，我即将坠入爱河，但它会爆炸并毁掉我的生活。但也没有其他办法。”</p><p> “所以坠入爱河有一种令人难以忘怀的品质。真的就像走进火圈一样。然后我认为这首歌的美妙之处，当你分解它时我也意识到，约翰尼·卡什的版本有节奏和所有其他东西。是他。它甚至可能是一首摇篮曲。但这适用于每首伟大的歌曲。这是一个经典。永恒的。”</p><p>李的最后一张专辑是 2022 年的《Eyeye》，这是她的第五张录音室唱片。 <i>《NME》</i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/lykke-li-eyeye-review-3227724">在一篇四星评论中</a>写道，它“更像是一首流行艺术情绪的作品，而不是单身人士的家”和“一张会呼吸、叹息的唱片，会让你迷失在这些曲目诞生时同样的茫然遐想中”从”。</p><p>艺术家本人将这张唱片称为“尝试将一生的浪漫痴迷和女性幻想压缩成超感官景观”，同时捕捉“服用大剂量LSD聆听语音备忘录的亲密感”。</p><p>李还在专辑发行后不久表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lykke-li-is-reworking-eyeye-into-an-ambient-instrumental-sonic-dream-3233521">，她计划“重新设计”这张专辑，使其“更像是一个环境、器乐、声音的梦想”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-lykke-lis-soulful-cover-of-johnny-cashs-ring-of-fire-3595762">《聆听 Lykke Li 深情翻唱 Johnny Cash 的《Ring Of Fire》》一文</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
