.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/charli_green_vincent-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/charli_green_vincent-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/st-vincent">St. Vincent</a>已被确认为今晚<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">全英音乐奖的</a>颁奖嘉宾。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="340" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-here-are-all-the-nominees-3576382"><b>2024 年全英音乐奖：以下是所有提名者</b></a></li></ul><p>颁奖典礼将于今晚（3 月 2 日）在伦敦 O2 剧场举行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maya-jama-among-the-new-hosts-for-the-brit-awards-2024-3581190">由玛雅·贾玛 (Maya Jama)、克拉拉·阿姆福 (Clara Amfo) 和罗曼·坎普 (Roman Kemp) 三位主持人主持</a>。该赛事可在 ITV1 和 ITVX 上观看。</p><p>圣文森特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/st-vincent-interview-broken-man-dave-grohl-new-album-all-born-screaming-listen-3594747">本周宣布了她的新专辑《All Born Screaming》</a> ，她将在全英红地毯秀上为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">《最后的晚宴》</a>颁发全英新星奖，该秀将由 ITV2 现场直播。 </p><figure id="attachment_3595743" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3595743" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3595743" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit_awards_2024.jpg" alt="（JM Enternational 2024 摄）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit_awards_2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit_awards_2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit_awards_2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit_awards_2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit_awards_2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/brit_awards_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3595743" class="wp-caption-text"> 2024 年全英音乐奖。<br /> （JM Enternational 2024 摄）</figcaption></figure><p> 2023 年底，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-brits-announce-2024-rising-star-winner-3555457">全英乐队宣布《最后的晚宴》获得了这一享有声望的奖项，并</a>得到了 BBC 广播 1 台的支持。</p><p>节目中的其他颁奖嘉宾包括 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-shares-club-ready-new-single-von-dutch-3594986">刚刚发行了新单曲“Von Dutch”的</a>Charli XCX，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/green-day-saviors-album-review-3567737">最近发行了最新专辑“Saviors”的</a>Green Day。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ashley-walters">阿什利·沃尔特斯 (Ashley Walters)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aitch">艾奇 (Aitch</a> )、杰米·温斯顿 (Jaime Winstone)、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/stranger-things"><i>《怪奇物语》</i></a>的乔·基瑞 (Joe Keery)、布里奇顿 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/bridgerton"><i>Bridgerton</i></a> ) 的乔纳森·贝利 (Jonathan Bailey)、《鲍勃·<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bob-marley"><i>马利：一个爱》(Bob Marley: One Love)</i></a>主演的金斯利·本-阿迪尔 (Kingsley Ben-Adir)、卢克·伊万斯 (Luke Evans) 以及即将上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse)</a>传记片的主演玛丽莎·阿贝拉 (Marisa Abela) 也将出席颁奖。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a>将现场表演拉开演出，Raye、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-announces-final-headliner-3591184">Tate McRae</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-announces-more-live-performers-for-2024-ceremony-3587758">Jungle、Rema、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-announces-becky-hill-and-chase-status-collab-performance-3588553">Becky Hill 和 Chase &amp; Status</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/calvin-harris-ellie-goulding-confirmed-to-perform-at-brit-awards-2024-3590433">Calvin Harris 和 Ellie Goulding</a>也将进行进一步表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kylie-minogue-to-receive-brits-global-icon-award-and-perform-at-ceremony-3586464">荣获今年全英音乐奖全球偶像奖的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kylie-minogue">凯莉·米洛 (Kylie Minogue)</a>也将以她自己的现场表演结束演出。</p><p>全英乐队已经在颁奖典礼前宣布了一些获奖者，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-announces-songwriter-of-the-year-winner-3594117">Raye 被确认为年度歌曲作者奖的获得者</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-responds-to-record-breaking-brit-award-nominations-3576851">这位歌手在演出中获得破纪录的七项奖项提名</a>，包括年度艺术家、万事达卡年度专辑（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/raye-my-21st-century-blues-review-3391162">《我的 21 世纪布鲁斯》</a> ）和最佳新人奖。</p><p> Raye 在谈到自己的获奖时表示：“说实话，我非常非常荣幸能够获得年度词曲作者奖，这是我第一次获得全英音乐奖，我会非常珍惜这个奖杯。</p><p>此外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-reveal-winner-of-producer-of-the-year-3592875">Chase &amp; Status 已被确认为 2024 年年度制作人雕像的获得者</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brits-2024-green-day-charli-xcx-and-st-vincent-announced-as-guest-presenters-3595748">BRITs 2024：Green Day 后，Charli XCX 和 St Vincent 宣布作为嘉宾主持人</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
